OL,5, A South Korean pastor once hailed as a 
OL,6, hero for smuggling out hundreds of     
OL,7, North Koreans has been jailed for      
OL,8, sexually abusing teenage defectors.    
OL,10,FChun Ki-won, 67, has been sentenced to 
OL,11,Ffive years for molesting minors at his 
OL,12,Fboarding school in Seoul.              
OL,14,FThe pastor had been viewed as a saviour
OL,15,Ffigure for decades with people calling 
OL,16,Fhim an "Asian Schindler" and his       
OL,17,Foperations an "Underground Railroad"   
OL,18,Ffor those fleeing the North's regime.  
OL,20,FHe was arrested in Seoul in September. 
